{
  "stem": "2226.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they didn't want to know-- nobody wants to walk close to us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So before we got inside in-- in the camp, we dumped the-- the branches so that-- we couldn't see.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were walking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We couldn't see nothing, because lots of people went back and forth with worker-- civil-- that way we shouldn't talk to them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we-- they shouldn't see us either.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we got over there, some-- some-- some SS come out, and some workers come out to see what's happen, what's going on with the-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The special shorts, the long blue and white-- you ever saw them-- them shorts?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The uniforms?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The uniforms, yeah-- blue and white.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I saw workers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, what's going on?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We come from over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No human being here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At least you can see it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He's cut nice, shaved, shoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So all of a sudden, a transfer, that they were-- they-- they were the same like me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe they come a few days before.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and they took us to the zone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And before we went into the zone, they told us everything-- everybody naked.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You should never keep even a hankie-- nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't have nothing, because everything was so-- so much lice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know where it's going.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we got into the zone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know what the zone is?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Tell us what is it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The zone is in a place where it's-- where-- disinfection.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there's hot water-- take the shower.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got in over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We got in over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We stand on a stool.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Women, men-- it don't make any difference-- all together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You stand on the stool, and they start to shave here, under the arm-- and start to shave here.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
